<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>Emilia Isabelle Euphemia Rose Clarke</em></strong> was born on 23 October 1986 and brought up in Berkshire London. She is the first daughter of her parents and has studied in <strong><em>Drama Center London</em></strong> through which she managed to perform in different stages. Her father was a theater sound Engineer who sadly passed away in 2016.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Career</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Emilia Clarke made her debut appearance as a guest star in one of the episodes on television series <strong><em>Soap Opera. </em></strong>Her performance in television and in the movie <strong><em>Triassic Attack</em></strong> titled her U.K star of tomorrow by Screen International magazine.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1440" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/jpbreakfast-jumbo-300x176.jpg" alt="" width="544" height="319" />
Clarke‚Äôs career got a break-through when she was cast as <strong><em>Daenerys Targaryen</em></strong> in <strong><em>Game of Thrones</em></strong> a fantastic HBO drama series.¬† She has also mentioned her funny as well as tedious experiences during the audition of Game of Thrones in some of her interviews.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1435" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/daenerys-season-six-finale-300x192.jpeg" alt="" width="546" height="349" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Starting her career from the small stage performances to the big Television series <strong><em>Game of Thrones </em></strong>in between she has been cast into different movies. Clarke‚Äôs talent can be seen in her movies too such as in the movie <em><strong>Spike Island</strong></em> which was released in 2012 just after her earlier project <strong><em>Game of Thrones </em></strong>season one. As she was known worldwide with the character name <strong><em>Khaleesi</em></strong> she has been much praised and admired globally for her role.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Coming into her movies after Spike Island, she has also done <strong><em>Dom Hemingway (2013), Terminator Genisys (2015), Me Before You (2016), Voice of Stone (2017). ¬†</em></strong></p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1436" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/MBY-7767rv2-300x201.jpg" alt="" width="533" height="357" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">Besides movies and series, she has also done a voice-over in different animation movies. She has given her voice to a character <strong><em>Marianne</em></strong> on animated series of <strong><em>Futurama </em></strong>and to a character <strong><em>Lumpy</em></strong> of Television series <strong><em>Animals.</em></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>¬†</em></strong><strong>Upcoming projects</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Emilia is a very talented actress she will continue to deliver her acting skills into movies and into the television series in the coming years. She is coming soon with two movies <strong><em>Above suspicion</em></strong> and <strong><em>A stars war story</em></strong> which are already under post-production and currently she is busy with her another movie <strong><em>The Beauty Inside</em></strong> which is under pre-production and she also will reprise her role in the final season of the massive hit <strong>HBO</strong> television series <strong><em>The Game of Thrones.</em></strong></p>
