<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>¬†</strong><strong>Personal Life</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">The passion for her acting was from very early age and she followed her dream and reached this peak of her career. She owns a house in a London and has also bought $4.64 million new home in Venice, California.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Emilia Clarke was in a relationship with a comedian and filmmaker <strong><em>Seth MacFarlane</em></strong> for about a year from 2012 to 2013.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-1445" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Emilia-Clarke-Seth-MacFarlane-Main-300x183.jpg" alt="" width="551" height="336" />

&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Achievements</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">This talented and expressive actress has achieved a lot of attention from her massive hit television series <strong><em>Game of Thrones</em></strong> through which she has been awarded for the <strong><em>female breakthrough performance</em></strong> in 2011. In the following year, she was also awarded as the <strong><em>Outstanding Female Rising star in Drama Series. </em></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Similarly, for her performance as <strong><em>Daenerys Targaryen </em></strong>in <strong><em>Game of Thrones</em></strong>, she was awarded as the <strong><em>Best Supportive Actress</em></strong> in 2012 and the <strong><em>Best Actress</em></strong> in the same year.</p>
